Name: Mausoleum of Khoja Ahmed Yasawi
Description: Mausoleum of Khoja Ahmed Yasawi - UNESCO World Heritage Site. Incomplete mausoleum built in the 14th century for the Sufi poet and philosopher Khoja Ahmed Yasawi.

Name: Western Tien-Shan
Description: Western Tien-Shan - UNESCO World Heritage Site. Transnational mountain range with exceptional biodiversity and unique ecosystems.

Name: Silk Roads: the Routes Network of Chang'an-Tianshan Corridor
Description: Silk Roads: the Routes Network of Chang'an-Tianshan Corridor - UNESCO World Heritage Site. Part of the extensive Silk Roads network connecting East and West.

Name: Cold Winter Deserts of Turan
Description: Cold Winter Deserts of Turan - UNESCO World Heritage Site. Unique desert ecosystem with exceptional biodiversity adapted to extreme cold winters.
